1
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:41,920
Your Majesty,

2
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:43,120
Prince Qi sent word

3
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:45,520
that the Empress is at his manor.

4
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:16,520
Do you plan to feed me

5
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:18,600
Ruanjin Powder forever?

6
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:20,720
Once Li Yunxi is dead,

7
00:02:22,760 --> 00:02:23,840
I will set you free.

8
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:53,720
He's here.

9
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:57,400
Cousin,

10
00:02:58,520 --> 00:02:59,579
how did the two of us

11
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:02,560
reach this point?

12
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:06,360
Don't you understand?

13
00:03:07,480 --> 00:03:10,080
That brotherly affection

14
00:03:11,320 --> 00:03:14,200
was just a facade all along.

15
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:27,400
Why did you bring her here?

16
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:30,840
She is two months pregnant.

17
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:33,360
The child is yours.

18
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:38,000
Cousin,

19
00:03:39,480 --> 00:03:41,440
I used Qingsirao on you back then,

20
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:43,460
but the child is innocent.

21
00:03:44,040 --> 00:03:45,280
Save me and the child.

22
00:03:47,160 --> 00:03:48,960
His Majesty refuses to touch me.

23
00:03:49,160 --> 00:03:50,440
I want a child.

24
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:57,640
Li Yunxi,

25
00:03:57,760 --> 00:04:00,620
I didn't expect you to use such despicable tactics.

26
00:04:00,920 --> 00:04:02,480
I can return her to you.

27
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:05,480
From now on, matters between us

28
00:04:05,600 --> 00:04:06,860
will not involve them.

29
00:04:08,640 --> 00:04:09,080
But

30
00:04:09,640 --> 00:04:11,040
I'm taking Aling.

31
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:13,760
Bring them in.

32
00:04:22,840 --> 00:04:23,360
A-Ling.

33
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,200
What did you do to her?

34
00:04:42,640 --> 00:04:43,840
She's with me.

35
00:04:44,960 --> 00:04:46,090
As for what she does,

36
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:48,800
that's up to me.

37
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:53,780
Swap someone else.

38
00:05:10,400 --> 00:05:10,960
A-Ling.

39
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:32,920
Li Yunmo.

40
00:05:33,400 --> 00:05:35,600
Useless pawns don't need to stay alive.

41
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:37,480
Is she to you...

42
00:05:38,320 --> 00:05:39,760
She is just a pawn.

43
00:05:43,440 --> 00:05:44,000
A'ling.

44
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:48,000
I can kill my own weakness

45
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:50,800
with my own hands.

46
00:05:51,840 --> 00:05:53,920
Can you bring yourself to kill

47
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:56,720
your own weakness?

48
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:57,840
Li Yunxi.

49
00:05:59,120 --> 00:05:59,960
Kill me.

50
00:06:01,080 --> 00:06:02,540
Don't let him control you.

51
00:06:29,880 --> 00:06:31,810
You don't even dare to kill a woman.

52
00:06:32,120 --> 00:06:33,720
Are you fit to be the Emperor?

53
00:06:45,400 --> 00:06:46,659
If you want the throne,

54
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:51,170
I will give it to you.

55
00:06:53,840 --> 00:06:54,640
Prince Qi,

56
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:56,840
this is the Imperial Edict His Majesty prepared

57
00:06:56,840 --> 00:06:58,370
before leaving the palace.

58
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:12,760
You planned to give up the throne all along.

59
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:17,120
What is honey to you,

60
00:07:18,280 --> 00:07:19,480
is poison to me.

61
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:23,160
To me, the throne

62
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:26,520
is meaningless.

63
00:07:28,760 --> 00:07:30,080
It is just a shackle.

64
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:39,600
I only want Aling.

65
00:07:48,320 --> 00:07:49,250
I won't be at ease

66
00:07:50,880 --> 00:07:52,080
until you are dead.

67
00:07:53,159 --> 00:07:54,880
As long as Xiao Ling is alive,

68
00:07:55,200 --> 00:07:56,480
she must be mine.

69
00:07:59,280 --> 00:08:00,360
A cup of arsenic

70
00:08:01,280 --> 00:08:03,080
to send Your Majesty on your way.

71
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:07,760
No!

72
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:11,160
So, Cousin,

73
00:08:13,320 --> 00:08:15,320
you never intended to let me live.

74
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:16,840
You can live,

75
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:20,520
but then Xiao Ling must die.

76
00:08:23,760 --> 00:08:24,440
Yunxi.

77
00:08:25,400 --> 00:08:26,080
No.

78
00:08:45,560 --> 00:08:46,120
Don't.

79
00:08:46,800 --> 00:08:47,440
Yunxi.

80
00:08:49,160 --> 00:08:49,640
Yunxi.

81
00:08:49,880 --> 00:08:50,480
Xiao Ling.

82
00:08:50,680 --> 00:08:51,280
Xiao Ling,

83
00:08:51,400 --> 00:08:52,160
look.

84
00:08:52,760 --> 00:08:53,880
Such an indecisive

85
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:55,400
and soft-hearted person

86
00:08:55,800 --> 00:08:57,040
is not worthy of you.

87
00:08:57,680 --> 00:08:58,810
I don't deserve you.

88
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:00,200
I don't deserve you.

89
00:09:00,280 --> 00:09:00,880
Don't.

90
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:02,400
Yunxi.

91
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:04,460
Don't drink it.

92
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:05,960
Trust me.

93
00:09:06,800 --> 00:09:08,560
I can fix this.

94
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:14,280
But I...

95
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,530
can't bear to leave you.

96
00:09:38,040 --> 00:09:39,360
No!

97
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:52,640
No.

98
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:01,680
Yunxi.

99
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:03,760
Yunxi.

100
00:10:06,920 --> 00:10:08,320
I told you not to drink it.

101
00:10:10,280 --> 00:10:11,640
Why are you so silly?

102
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:14,880
Don't cry.

103
00:10:17,960 --> 00:10:19,520
I'm finally free.

104
00:10:20,520 --> 00:10:22,680
I grew tired of the hatred

105
00:10:24,120 --> 00:10:25,980
and the Imperial Palace long ago.

106
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:27,640
Ling.

107
00:10:28,840 --> 00:10:29,760
In this life,

108
00:10:30,880 --> 00:10:32,280
My greatest luck

109
00:10:33,560 --> 00:10:35,440
was having you by my side.

110
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:36,840
But...

111
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:39,520
I failed you.

112
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:43,040
If there is a next life,

113
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:46,440
let's be an ordinary couple.

114
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:51,880
Take me to Jiangnan.

115
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:54,160
Will you?

116
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:56,080
Okay.

117
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:58,660
I'll take you to Jiangnan.

118
00:11:00,320 --> 00:11:01,480
I'll take you there.

119
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:03,800
Good.

120
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:23,600
Yunxi.

121
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:26,160
We won't go home until we're drunk.

122
00:11:26,160 --> 00:11:28,090
We won't go home until we're drunk.

123
00:11:31,720 --> 00:11:33,600
The Emperor stole your father's throne,

124
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:36,120
yet you call the Crown Prince your brother every day.

125
00:11:36,120 --> 00:11:38,120
How could I have such a disappointing son?

126
00:11:38,120 --> 00:11:39,200
Useless thing.

127
00:11:39,320 --> 00:11:40,080
Trash.

128
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:41,520
How do you have the nerve to live?

129
00:11:41,520 --> 00:11:43,160
I shouldn't have raised you.

130
00:11:43,360 --> 00:11:44,120
Trash.

131
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:47,880
His Majesty

132
00:11:53,560 --> 00:11:55,520
has passed away.

133
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:17,960
Why didn't I die this time?

134
00:12:26,320 --> 00:12:27,200
Perhaps...

135
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:30,450
I still have a chance to save everyone.

136
00:12:46,320 --> 00:12:47,050
What is that?

137
00:12:51,920 --> 00:12:53,050
Where did you get it?

138
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:03,120
You're weak right now.

139
00:13:03,880 --> 00:13:04,880
You can't kill me.

140
00:13:11,240 --> 00:13:12,640
What are you laughing at?

141
00:13:12,760 --> 00:13:14,040
I can't kill you.

142
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:17,060
What are you doing?

143
00:13:21,080 --> 00:13:22,840
But I can kill myself.

144
00:13:24,680 --> 00:13:26,040
You'd rather die?

145
00:13:27,520 --> 00:13:29,560
Not even willing to be my Empress?

146
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:31,680
I, Xiao Ling,

147
00:13:32,160 --> 00:13:34,090
have only one husband in this life.

148
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:36,560
That is Li Yunxi.

149
00:13:53,200 --> 00:13:55,660
Why is there only half an incense stick left?

150
00:13:57,280 --> 00:13:57,840
Who is it?

151
00:14:10,840 --> 00:14:12,840
Does it mean as long as the incense burns,

152
00:14:12,840 --> 00:14:14,100
I can come back to life?

153
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:20,800
Your Majesty.

154
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:23,440
His Majesty is holding a banquet at Qinghuan Pavilion tonight.

155
00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:24,200
He invites you to attend.

156
00:14:24,200 --> 00:14:24,960
Your Majesty.

157
00:14:24,960 --> 00:14:25,890
I'll go find him.

158
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:29,520
Your Majesty, where are you going?

159
00:14:29,520 --> 00:14:31,180
At least change your clothes.

160
00:14:40,880 --> 00:14:41,640
Yunxi.

161
00:15:10,360 --> 00:15:12,440
Li Yunxi has no memory of his past four lives.

162
00:15:12,440 --> 00:15:14,370
I'll scare him off if I'm too eager.

163
00:15:14,640 --> 00:15:15,840
After all, right now,

164
00:15:15,880 --> 00:15:19,010
he still bears the feud between the Xiao and Li families.

165
00:15:20,520 --> 00:15:21,600
I came to tell you

166
00:15:22,120 --> 00:15:23,580
that I'm not feeling well,

167
00:15:23,920 --> 00:15:26,450
so I can't attend the palace banquet tonight.

168
00:15:32,320 --> 00:15:32,800
Okay.

169
00:16:08,400 --> 00:16:09,400
I was reborn.

170
00:16:10,320 --> 00:16:12,320
Could it be related to this incense?

171
00:16:12,760 --> 00:16:14,890
But why is there only half a stick left?

172
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:16,680
Where did this incense come from?

173
00:16:16,680 --> 00:16:18,560
Why have I never noticed it before?

174
00:16:18,560 --> 00:16:20,720
My Lady, you've been staring at this spot since you returned.

175
00:16:20,720 --> 00:16:22,480
Did I not clean it properly?

176
00:16:25,520 --> 00:16:26,450
You can't see it?

177
00:16:31,440 --> 00:16:32,320
See what?

178
00:16:37,760 --> 00:16:38,360
Nothing.

179
00:16:43,920 --> 00:16:45,520
Could it be that this incense

180
00:16:45,560 --> 00:16:47,890
can only be seen by someone reborn like me?

181
00:16:49,080 --> 00:16:49,940
No matter what,

182
00:16:50,640 --> 00:16:52,300
this time, I must be with Yunxi

183
00:16:52,560 --> 00:16:54,120
forever.
